data.description: WELCOME HOME: to this "MOVE IN READY"! Agents, please bring your buyers to see this Three Level, Three Bedroom and Three Bathroom Home. This home is situated on a large corner lot with a Spacious Main Living Area, Bright and Open with New Carpet. The Gourmet Kitchen has Wood-Countertops and Dining area with access to the Wooden-Deck equipped with an attached Garden Pergola with stairs that lead to the backyard! The Lower-Level features a Sprawling family Room, a Laundry Room and Full Bath which connects to the Three-Car Garage. The home features a HVAC installed 2021 with 5year warranty and brand-new roof installed two years ago.  Brand new roof installed in June of 2021. The home is located a few minutes from downtown Annapolis and right off Highway 50.  Which means you are a stone's throw away from Sandy Beach and the Iconic Chesapeake Bay Bridge.   Schedule a showing today!
